Class RemoteAccessResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jbei.ice.services.rest.RestResource
      • org.jbei.ice.services.rest.RemoteAccessResource

  • @Path(value="/remote/{id}")
public class RemoteAccessResource
extends RestResource
    REST resource for sending/retrieving messages from remote ICE instances. Local instances access this resource which contacts the remote resource on its behalf
